description:
A new story begins: 'End Times'!

The Avengers are picking up the pieces after their war with the X-Men, but an old enemy has them in his sights and he wants them humiliated and destroyed!

By Brian Michael Bendis, Walt Simonson, Carlos Pacheco and Michael Avon Oeming.

Reprints:

  • Avengers #30.
  • New Avengers #30-33.

Contains:

  • The Return of Kaos Moon : Song of the Siren written & illustrated by David Boller
  • The Wallas: Big Lizard in My Backyard written & illustrated by Mary Hildebrandt; inks by David Boller
  • Tribal Tech: The Dervishes of Far-el-haq written & Illustrated by David Boller
  • Half-Moon: Owl's Pray written and illustrated by Mary Hildebrandt; inks by David Boller

description:
Following the events of FOREVER EVIL, Superman confronts Lex Luthor but the world has turned around for these two. The hero has become the villain and the villain the hero as forces beyond these two gather to destroy the Man of Steel, beginning with a dormant Doomsday who has crossed over from the Phantom Zone!

Note: Parasite appears only on the Mad Magazine Variant.
name: Unbound

description: A FUTURES END prelude! Spinning out of AQUAMAN, the King of Atlantis and his teammates find themselves targeted by an unknown foe that wants their Atlantean artifacts! Dont miss the start of this all-new series!
name: Legacy of Gold, Part I of V

description: Batwing races Menace to attempt to save his family! But the Gotham Underground is about to boil over with anarchy, and no matter which tribe rises up from below Gotham City, Batwing will be the first target!
name: Underbelly

description:
A bold new direction for DETECTIVE COMICS as THE FLASH creative team of Francis Manapul and Brian Buccelato take over the creative reins! Batman finds himself knee-deep in a new mystery involving a deadly new narcotic that has hit the streets of Gotham City.
